{"tid":1420473,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聯署要求美國將警務處列為恐怖組織","createTime":"2019-08-06T04:41:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T23:49:50.000Z","uid":300023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2dca9b621acb85694eedb8cc2c09a983df50a1c3","tid":1420473,"uid":300023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:41:31.000Z","msg":"關於香港警務處由6月至今的對應和平集會遊行的暴力行動，並針對7月21日的元朗白衣人黑社會幫會恐怖襲擊及8月4日對被補少女的性暴力行為，請協助聯署一份於美國白宮官網 &ldquo;We The People&rdquo; 的請願書，敦促美國政府將香港警務處列為恐怖組織。請按回複驗證郵件中的超連結來確認聯署。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fofficially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization&d=NNqT6wnuCkALqD5scUUSnIbCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=7a77c531\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization</a><br />\n<br />\n希望值此聯署逼使美國及其他西方民主國家對該恐怖組織採取實質行動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1419709\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1419709</a>"},{"pid":"9a51c9e3bd312a6147aa4db7c2fe8a7f1b8d42a8","tid":1420473,"uid":300023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:21:19.000Z","msg":"中國共產黨、中央政府、中聯辦、港澳辦、娥特、特區黑警宜家口口聲聲的「恐怖主義」苗頭，就是因為要撐住香港警察行使「恐怖主義」來「止暴制亂*」。極權政府最喜歡打壓人民，但也最害怕被標籤為「恐怖主義」。警隊已經使用新納粹份子常使用的「老鼠」、「蟑螂」、「曱甴」等來打壓異見人士，請加入美國白宮聯署打擊這種滅火人性的恐怖組織。<br />\n*止 - 止住善良；暴 - 暴力襲擊；制 - 制造恐慌；亂 - 亂從警來。<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fofficially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization&d=NNqT6wnuCkALqD5scUUSnIbCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=7a77c531\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization</a>"},{"pid":"807ceef56b9dd4c829fcfc35ab73d99004e8568b","tid":1420473,"uid":300023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:49:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3983a4610dc1c36f616c62bf948ae5e59e693f6d","tid":1420473,"uid":300023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T04:26:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kysbKDq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkysbKDq.png&h=08153dc1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2aff35ede7ec3eb41a6e100fdd2c73b27f979370","tid":1420473,"uid":300023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T05:37:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KcaEqts.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKcaEqts.png&h=1768b98c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd3714568d776bb25c4aea011dd0b6ca351f678a","tid":1420473,"uid":300023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:45:38.000Z","msg":"166,641<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BTfMSh9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBTfMSh9.png&h=b46e19dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac07d9f6b632fd58b840c17ba7f4253071b4c815","tid":1420473,"uid":300023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:04:29.000Z","msg":"166,665<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QJDiKvR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQJDiKvR.png&h=ffe9f721&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ddbfe1382c0df363a5bd9a3e099d9e32e54206cd","tid":1420473,"uid":300023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T23:48:10.000Z","msg":"166,701<br />